    {
      "id": "33",
      "name": "Gallery",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "gallery_character",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "img": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/10/20/94376896/6db00a617388f6c6284047754da6199b_1605224828181604312.jpg",
                "imgDesc": "<p>You will sometimes encounter Teleport Waypoint and Domain Entrance Map Pins bearing such sub-icons.</p><p>These symbols indicate that the destination is located in a multi-layered area. After you unlock the corresponding map layer, you can interact with said pins to open the corresponding sub-map.</p>",
                "key": "Page 1/5"
              },
              {
                "img": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/10/20/94376896/3a0782dc2964b7dabc08021f2816980c_3760413830641048709.jpg",
                "imgDesc": "<p>Use the layer markers on the right side of the Map interface to switch between layers within the same group or select the big icon to return to the top-level map.</p>",
                "key": "Page 2/5"
              },
              {
                "img": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/10/20/94376896/a12e8f19c1bea260db62bff7c1460102_3697290003028110514.jpg",
                "imgDesc": "<p>When browsing map layers, the sub-icon of the Map Pin(s) for the current layer will appear in bright blue.</p>",
                "key": "Page 3/5"
              },
              {
                "img": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/10/20/94376896/1f1a121f45bf88458d72e51b12232447_5004274717469657687.jpg",
                "imgDesc": "<p>Dotted lines will be used for indicators (Quest targets, Event targets, etc.) that are not located in the current map layer.</p>",
                "key": "Page 4/5"
              },
              {
                "img": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/10/20/94376896/117f60c2bc2b621e9b7089f326b78bea_7390290065986252923.jpg",
                "imgDesc": "<p>Additionally, when an area in the center of the map contains different layers that you have previously entered, you can use the layer-switching marker to swap over to the corresponding map.</p>",
                "key": "Page 5/5"
              }
            ],
            "pic": ""
          }
        }
      ]
